I beg to move, in line 5, to leave out the word "approved," and to add instead thereof:
disapproved, inasmuch as they should be subject to the following modifications, namely:—
In First Schedule—


30s. should be inserted for 24s.;

20s. should be inserted for 16s. and 15s.;

18 years should be inserted for 21 years;

20s. should be inserted for 10s. and 9s. for members of the household over 18 years of age;

10s. should be inserted for 8s. or 6s. for members of the household over 14 years
